{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 3,
  "title": "第三章（安民）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "不上賢，使民不爭。不貴難得之貨，使民不為盜。不見可欲，使民不亂。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人之治也：虛亓心，實亓腹，弱亓志，強亓骨。"
    },
    {
      "text": "恆使民无知无欲也，使夫知不敢。弗為而已，則无不治矣。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 4,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不爭功名，返自然也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言人君不御好珍寶，黃金棄於山，珠玉捐於淵也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "上化清靜，下無貪人。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 24,
          "end": 25
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "放鄭聲，遠美人。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 32,
          "end": 32
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不邪淫，不惑亂也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 9,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "說聖人治國與治身同也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 18,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "除嗜欲，去亂煩。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 22,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "懷道抱一守，五神也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 26,
          "end": 27
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "和柔謙讓，不處權也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 30,
          "end": 31
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "愛精重施，髓滿骨堅。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 22,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "返樸守淳。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 26,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "思慮深，不輕言。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 26,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不造作，動因循。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 43,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "德化厚，百姓安。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 32,
          "end": 32
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "賢，猶能也。尚者，嘉之名也。貴者，隆之稱也。唯能是任，尚也曷為；唯用是施，貴之何為。尚賢顯名，榮過其任，為而常校，能相射貴貨，過用貪者，競趣穿窬探篋，沒命而盜，故可欲不見，則心無所亂也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 9,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "心懷智而腹懷食，虛有智而實無知也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 26,
          "end": 27
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "骨無知以幹，志生事以亂，心虛則志弱也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 22,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "守其真也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 26,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "知者謂知為也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 26,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
